headline: Corpay Cross-Border Extends Partnership with World Aquatics
summary: TORONTO, November 18, 2024--Corpay, Inc.*, (NYSE: CPAY) a global leader in corporate payments, is pleased to announce that Corpay’s Cross-Border business has entered into a multi-year agreement to extend their successful collaboration with World Aquatics as their Official FX Payments Supplier.
